Some of the old dinos here can confirm that people used to say it is 24 (when 20th nuke was awful), then it was 34, then it settled to 50 for about 9 months. Then Kunark came out and few months after that the rumor of 60 being the must level started. Then in Luclin it was about AA. Now with again increased cap in PoP, people are saying 65. Well, of course they are. That's how the game and population progresses.<br>
